      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">26.104</ph> Contract clause.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d1714e8" class="- topic/p ">Contracting officers in civilian agencies may insert the clause at <xref href="52.226-1.dita#FAR_52_226_1"
                  base="i1054968"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "/>, Utilization of Indian Organizations and Indian-Owned Economic Enterprises, in solicitations and contracts if-</p>
         <ol id="d1684e22" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1707e15">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            In the opinion of the contracting officer, subcontracting possibilities exist for Indian organizations or Indian-owned economic enterprises; and</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1707e20">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            Funds are available for any increased costs as described in paragraph (b)(2) of the clause at <xref href="52.226-1.dita#FAR_52_226_1"
                        base="i1054968"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref "/>.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
